> Developed with Gatsby

<h1>Usage </h1>

1.  **Install the Gatsby CLI.**
  ```shell
    npm install -g gatsby-cli
    ```

1.  **Install NPM packages.**
  ```shell
    npm install
    ```

3.  **Install NPM packages.**
  ```shell
    npm run dev
    ```

    Your site is now running at http://localhost:8000!
